<item>
            <title>[LU-339] add configure check for MS_HAS_NEW_AOPS to support new aops</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-339</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;from RHEL5.3, old and new aops coexist, and a flag MS_HAS_NEW_AOPS is use to mark whether a filesystem supports new aops. Lustre has implmented new aops, but this flag is not set.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="10890">LU-339</key>
            <summary>add configure check for MS_HAS_NEW_AOPS to support new aops</summary>
